"You step into air then plummet into a deep pit, the home of a rat pack.">)
	       (T 
		<SETG ON-BEAM T>
		<MOVE ,BEAM ,WEST-END-OF-PASSAGE>
		,WEST-END-OF-PASSAGE)>>

